text:
> Texas Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win Houston Astros starting pitcher Dallas Keuchel, right, is greeted by manager A.J. Hinch after striking out Kansas City Royals' Lorenzo Cain during the seventh inning in Game 3 of baseball's American League Division Series Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Houston. (AP Photo/Pat Sullivan)
